{"title":"TripGenie | OTA行业AI设计探索","slug":"yn10pglogyfgpou5","summary":"2023年被誉为人工智能的“元年”，自ChatGPT发布以来，生成式AI技术迅猛发展，推动多个行业 实现突破性变革。在这一背景下，在线旅游（OTA）行业也迎来新一轮技术升级与体验重塑的重要契机。我们开始深入思考：如何将AI能力与旅游服务场景深度融合，以智能化的方式提升行程规划、商","category":"2. 国内产品","tags":["PART6️⃣ AI产品设计案例分析库","2. 国内产品"],"featured":false,"order":93,"level":2,"updatedAt":"2025-09-25","wordCount":1794,"sourceUrl":"https://www.yuque.com/abyssalsailor/yg90qa/yn10pglogyfgpou5","html":"<p data-lake-id=\"ucaf557ba\" id=\"ucaf557ba\" style=\"text-align: left\"><em><span data-lake-id=\"ub904dfeb\" id=\"ub904dfeb\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">2023年被誉为人工智能的“元年”，自ChatGPT发布以来，生成式AI技术迅猛发展，推动多个行业</span></em><em><span data-lake-id=\"u2ce2fa88\" id=\"u2ce2fa88\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">实现突破性变革。在这一背景下，在线旅游（OTA）行业也迎来新一轮技术升级与体验重塑的重要契机。我们开始深入思考：如何将AI能力与旅游服务场景深度融合，以智能化的方式提升行程规划、商品预订以及出行服务的体验？基于这一目标，我们设计并开发了内嵌于</span></em><em><span data-lake-id=\"u6442c2fc\" id=\"u6442c2fc\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(40, 125, 250)\">Trip.com</span></em><em><span data-lake-id=\"ua86a6fd3\" id=\"ua86a6fd3\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">的AI旅行助手工具——TripGenie。该工具致力于为用户提供个性化、沉浸式的旅行解决方案，覆盖目的地推荐、行程规划、旅游资讯问答等环节。接下来，让我们一同回顾 TripGenie 的设计历程。</span></em></p><p data-lake-id=\"ucc1358f7\" id=\"ucc1358f7\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1758805237275-221792ea-4fee-4ee9-a36e-badd9092eff6.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22uc6e77a11-13a6-421e-a620-a7b4a15166a%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u08c11f78-ff2d-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23d3e4f9%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22udb2c0ee0%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"975e182d\" id=\"975e182d\" style=\"text-align: left\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua7a573a7\" id=\"ua7a573a7\" class=\"lake-fontsize-16\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">1.0 版本：奠定基础，抢占先机</span></strong></h1><p data-lake-id=\"ud752915e\" id=\"ud752915e\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1758805237347-f3dc5351-040c-40a4-acc6-ce39be85e0e5.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u7e7babfe-ecbd-40da-b8ad-d9a25f86a81%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u08c11f78-ff2d-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23121311%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u68094f36%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"uc89ff764\" id=\"uc89ff764\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue0ef9ce1\" id=\"ue0ef9ce1\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">2023 年初，Trip.com开启了 TripGenie 1.0 版本的探索。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u06530df6\" id=\"u06530df6\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1f303368\" id=\"u1f303368\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">我们快速搭建了一个基础的 AI 对话框架，来满足基本的对话需求。同年 2 月，以最快速度上线了 TripGenie 的 MVP 版本，成为 OTA 行业内首个集成 ChatGPT 的 AI 旅行助手。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ud92724ed\" id=\"ud92724ed\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1758805237331-6ceffa9d-7407-4b02-b1a0-f9383a3c25f3.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ued267242-5052-4912-98d3-e5da4a60fbe%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u08c11f78-ff2d-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%2306213d%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22udae4bb99%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"6753511b\" id=\"6753511b\" style=\"text-align: left\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u57639d45\" id=\"u57639d45\" class=\"lake-fontsize-16\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">2.0 版本：优化体验与提升流量并行</span></strong></h1><p data-lake-id=\"u6639dfc1\" id=\"u6639dfc1\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1758805237303-38b9a6aa-781c-4271-85f3-fcf4083b57ba.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u72a83b50-763a-4dc0-a8eb-486a59ae15c%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u08c11f78-ff2d-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23050604%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ufccfe872%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u461f9305\" id=\"u461f9305\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"udf7480f2\" id=\"udf7480f2\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">随着用户数量的增多，1.0 版本的基础对话框架和内容已无法满足用户诉求，优化使用体验变得尤为迫切。于是我们开启了 TripGenie 2.0 版本的探索。此版本旨在为用户提供更优体验，同时进一步提升 TripGenie 的使用流量。</span></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"521d43ac\" id=\"521d43ac\" style=\"text-align: left\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc8482d28\" id=\"uc8482d28\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">1.体验</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u91bf7096\" id=\"u91bf7096\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">优化：让用户爱上提问</span></strong></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u7ab03be0\" id=\"u7ab03be0\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u979af248\" id=\"u979af248\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">我们的核心优化策略是为用户提供「更有价值的信息」、「流畅的对话方式」以及「舒适的阅读体验」。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ufd8877e9\" id=\"ufd8877e9\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1758805237352-87b7cf33-9274-49d2-88b8-2f3a805b1265.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u0459d857-6f2b-49a7-b3c8-2127dbf22ee%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u08c11f78-ff2d-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A425%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23050504%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uee0d29ee%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"udf89a973\" id=\"udf89a973\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub83e6155\" id=\"ub83e6155\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">(1)</span><span data-lake-id=\"ua0246df0\" id=\"ua0246df0\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">提供更有价值的信息</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u852e7931\" id=\"u852e7931\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud33c3823\" id=\"ud33c3823\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">例如，在TripGenie1.0 版本中，当用户查询机票时，TripGenie 仅能引导用户到</span><span data-lake-id=\"u1dab27de\" id=\"u1dab27de\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(40, 125, 250)\">Trip.com</span><span data-lake-id=\"u1d96418f\" id=\"u1d96418f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">的机票列表页搜索预订。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u3d8ee8fe\" id=\"u3d8ee8fe\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6c8edaf9\" id=\"u6c8edaf9\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">而TripGenie2.0 版本与平台内的信息和资源打通；针对机票问题，不仅能为用户提供跳转到搜索列表的入口，还会提供出行建议；并在回答的最后，推荐常用的快捷筛选条件入口，为用户带来更友好的体验。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u9d5678bd\" id=\"u9d5678bd\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1758805237857-c4cb7822-e597-43b5-a00f-4e2cc3fbe42a.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u8c8737c7-5ae7-43f7-807e-7c3d0ef9627%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u08c11f78-ff2d-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23625f52%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ub48fb4e7%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"c36df4ae\" id=\"c36df4ae\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u97b70866\" id=\"u97b70866\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">(2)</span><span data-lake-id=\"ue14ccd63\" id=\"ue14ccd63\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">提供流畅的对话方式</span></h3><ul list=\"u0a9a8952\"><li fid=\"uba019571\" data-lake-id=\"u099baa48\" id=\"u099baa48\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufcde188a\" id=\"ufcde188a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">在用户提问前，通过TripGenie的自我介绍和预置问题推荐，让用户快速认识TripGenie并开启对话；</span></li><li fid=\"uba019571\" data-lake-id=\"u8058a0b0\" id=\"u8058a0b0\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"uea08a82f\" id=\"uea08a82f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">在对话中，为用户提供选项卡片；例如用户想取消订单时，直接在对话里展示订单卡片，提升对话效率；</span></li><li fid=\"uba019571\" data-lake-id=\"u69fd4d83\" id=\"u69fd4d83\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub744d81a\" id=\"ub744d81a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">当一轮问答结束后，提供关联问题推荐，引导用户进行多轮对话。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u2aaeac75\" id=\"u2aaeac75\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u27a96a63\" id=\"u27a96a63\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">通过这些优化，人均对话轮次得到大幅的提升。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ube30aa87\" id=\"ube30aa87\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1758805237812-4290af00-9924-48f0-8228-f2974dc921f1.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22uc21e94ce-3e8a-4495-9ded-c89bd9db8a7%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u08c11f78-ff2d-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%2378756f%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u912730ba%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"f59b1138\" id=\"f59b1138\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u33548157\" id=\"u33548157\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">(3)</span><span data-lake-id=\"u542dc1ca\" id=\"u542dc1ca\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">提供舒适的阅读体验</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"ua0a89a24\" id=\"ua0a89a24\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3f31dc0e\" id=\"u3f31dc0e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">在阅读体验上，随着 TripGenie 覆盖意图增多，许多场景的回答篇幅过长，尤其在西语场景下，篇幅超过 2 屏，仅按 AI 输出的文本格式展示，可读性极差。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u0d0eaa48\" id=\"u0d0eaa48\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2f036a81\" id=\"u2f036a81\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">为此，我们对回答文本进行格式化输出，制定了字号、行高、字重等基础规范，还定义了统一的段间距及项目符号列表的使用场景，使长文本段落层级更清晰，阅读体验更顺畅。此外，用户调研显示，90% 的用户认为图文穿插的内容易读性更高，因此我们在长文本中加入图片展示。一系列优化后，用户满意度大幅提升。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ud339b0c9\" id=\"ud339b0c9\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1758805237854-89c7fa93-e675-4f25-9052-47a076dc5e67.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u2340ebe1-c48e-446b-8f0d-03461f0439a%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u08c11f78-ff2d-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23a9aba9%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u6bd03550%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"a12edb4e\" id=\"a12edb4e\" style=\"text-align: left\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u37434c1e\" id=\"u37434c1e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">2.</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua0aebbd0\" id=\"ua0aebbd0\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">提升流量：拓展多场景触点</span></strong></h2><p data-lake-id=\"uc8f11915\" id=\"uc8f11915\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u961c04e6\" id=\"u961c04e6\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">为获取更多用户流量，我们积极扩展触点。</span></p><ul list=\"u1f2e1f24\"><li fid=\"u832b5ad1\" data-lake-id=\"ua543f299\" id=\"ua543f299\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9eaa2758\" id=\"u9eaa2758\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">在页面场景上，已在 Moments 的内容页、My Trips 页面、POI 页面增加了 TripGenie 的悬浮入口；</span></li><li fid=\"u832b5ad1\" data-lake-id=\"uc9c36aad\" id=\"uc9c36aad\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u13e46f71\" id=\"u13e46f71\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">还会按主题场景向用户呈现更丰富的样式：如根据不同站点的重要节庆日，对TripGenie悬浮按钮进行主题包装，并通过欢迎语营造节日氛围；</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u8d46f0f2\" id=\"u8d46f0f2\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue641b954\" id=\"ue641b954\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">对比默认入口，按场景化触达的悬浮按钮入口点击率有明显提升。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u8ae348e4\" id=\"u8ae348e4\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1758805237807-13d37d61-6574-4c05-b12a-15c77e138e71.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u59a715c0-a661-4401-852b-0947121175d%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u08c11f78-ff2d-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23434744%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u33c88876%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u3be0b691\" id=\"u3be0b691\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1ddc954b\" id=\"u1ddc954b\" class=\"lake-fontsize-16\" style=\"color: rgb(26, 36, 255)\">03</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue068c022\" id=\"ue068c022\" class=\"lake-fontsize-16\" style=\"color: rgb(253, 166, 9)\">.</span></strong></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"189bf8fc\" id=\"189bf8fc\" style=\"text-align: left\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub4cf7fb1\" id=\"ub4cf7fb1\" class=\"lake-fontsize-16\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">3.0 版本：场景拓展与功能深化</span></strong></h1><p data-lake-id=\"uea365c82\" id=\"uea365c82\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1758805237811-0c64aa7e-5859-4751-86e5-2a5bd1be22ff.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ud897364b-a1d6-466b-b4d3-33f532496b7%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u08c11f78-ff2d-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%230b0c0a%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uaa7741d8%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u3ee41fee\" id=\"u3ee41fee\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufe96401d\" id=\"ufe96401d\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">进入 3.0 阶段，我们致力于扩展更多使用场景。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uc5f5fb87\" id=\"uc5f5fb87\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u55022328\" id=\"u55022328\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">我们与综合搜索深度融合，过去的传统搜索更多依赖关键词匹配，难以理解用户背后的真实意图。引入 TripGenie 后，借助 AI 对复杂自然语言的理解能力，能够围绕用户的具体任务提供更智能的协同支持。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ub6879506\" id=\"ub6879506\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u50d2c4a5\" id=\"u50d2c4a5\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">以用户搜索 “5天4晚的东京行程，最后一天购物” 为例，传统搜索只能返回相关帖子和商品，无法满足用户对行程整体规划的个性化需求。而接入 TripGenie 后，可以通过嵌入式模块展示 AI 生成的定制化路线，协助用户完成更复杂的任务目标，同时匹配更多维度的搜索结果。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u9b685916\" id=\"u9b685916\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1758805238251-9c0b300b-8e67-4eb8-ac31-43a7db8ebc41.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ud721806b-e24d-47d6-b3b4-fccb738c37d%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u08c11f78-ff2d-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23a49c87%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u58ea05a3%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u011180b2\" id=\"u011180b2\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u261e57bc\" id=\"u261e57bc\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">除了与现有功能融合外，TripGenie也在不断探索新功能，解决用户行中的问题。目前已在 TripGenie 内上线了菜单助手、图片识别、实时翻译等工具，并在大部分站点上线了实时导览功能。这些工具主要被用来应对境外旅行中遇到的语言问题；并且 TripGenie 已经将部分功能扩展至了系统级的Widget组件中，使得用户可以在需要它们的场合更快、更便捷的找到它们。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"udfd89bac\" id=\"udfd89bac\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1758805238259-394cdec8-ee6d-4f8f-b81b-ea90bf7bae7a.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u8bcf984a-2c0b-4373-9bab-31e07d21e1b%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u08c11f78-ff2d-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%239b9177%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ua492f38a%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u8b428468\" id=\"u8b428468\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1758805238318-38a13d22-e354-4cbb-8736-75499ea62830.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u2364b9bb-d75b-4170-98be-bd7de99f26c%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u08c11f78-ff2d-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23090908%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u9e372d73%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"uf9cfd3fe\" id=\"uf9cfd3fe\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0f523c23\" id=\"u0f523c23\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">另外，为了进一步提升流量、扩展更多的使用渠道，我们上线了Web 版的 TripGenie，以承接网页端的流量。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u8c7d515e\" id=\"u8c7d515e\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1758805238384-f7382b8f-d723-49c7-9729-b94cc2347fe6.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u377705de-de64-4837-876d-af106003ba4%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u08c11f78-ff2d-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23222222%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ua99cdb5f%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"39fbf54c\" id=\"39fbf54c\" style=\"text-align: left\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc704ef39\" id=\"uc704ef39\" class=\"lake-fontsize-16\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">总结与成果</span></strong></h1><p data-lake-id=\"u2b958f0d\" id=\"u2b958f0d\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u668a7825\" id=\"u668a7825\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">回顾 TripGenie 的发展，我们在搭建了基础的 AI 对话框架后，先后经历了体验优化、流量提升、场景扩展三个阶段。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ubb00a179\" id=\"ubb00a179\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1758805238368-42385905-3979-485d-85ce-d16aa76d048e.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ud81a9ed6-84e0-4a73-a289-d87d77fc3d2%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u08c11f78-ff2d-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23646563%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u0b1674d8%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"ubb54ea8d\" id=\"ubb54ea8d\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7dabd7bd\" id=\"u7dabd7bd\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">截至目前，TripGenie 积累了大量提问用户，日均流量较年初有显著增长，峰值流量可观，人均停留时长也大幅增加。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u5e344258\" id=\"u5e344258\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub48f3ae6\" id=\"ub48f3ae6\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">此外，</span><span data-lake-id=\"ud17bf917\" id=\"ud17bf917\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(40, 125, 250)\">Trip.com</span><span data-lake-id=\"u0b2bba49\" id=\"u0b2bba49\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">荣获了日本 G mark 2024设计大奖，TripGenie 作为重要功能参评并获得评委好评；同时，</span><span data-lake-id=\"uc109829f\" id=\"uc109829f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(40, 125, 250)\">Trip.com</span><span data-lake-id=\"u7520e16e\" id=\"u7520e16e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"> 还因为 TripGenie 上榜了Skift idea award 的 Finalist，上榜理由为 Best use of AI，这些都是我们取得的成果。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u4e9569d3\" id=\"u4e9569d3\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1758805238719-e6f29a10-edf7-44bc-9f4a-d42412105d0d.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u7ea78462-3683-413f-851f-98c77412924%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u08c11f78-ff2d-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%230e0d09%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uabc1bcae%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u031e5ed0\" id=\"u031e5ed0\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6be27036\" id=\"u6be27036\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">未来，我们将继续探索AI技术与旅行结合的无限可能，让TripGenie成为每一位旅行者不可或缺的智慧伙伴。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u770fdb0f\" id=\"u770fdb0f\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufcadbb61\" id=\"ufcadbb61\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">​</span><br></p><blockquote data-lake-id=\"u9fa515c7\" id=\"u9fa515c7\"><p data-lake-id=\"u5eda2483\" id=\"u5eda2483\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u325a3a01\" id=\"u325a3a01\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">原文链接：</span><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/7omHeElwySbT9EV-aUd4-Q\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u5212e0aa\" id=\"u5212e0aa\"><span data-lake-id=\"udedf3a1e\" id=\"udedf3a1e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/7omHeElwySbT9EV-aUd4-Q</span></a></p></blockquote>"}
